        <section class="section">
            <h2>Technical Implementation</h2>
            <p><strong>Server Infrastructure:</strong> This website is deployed on Microsoft Azure using Infrastructure as a Service (IaaS). The server runs on a Linux environment with Nginx web server, secured with SSL/TLS encryption via Let's Encrypt.</p>
            <p><strong>Technology Stack:</strong> Static HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript ensure fast loading times and optimal performance across all devices.</p>
            <p><strong>Security:</strong> Implemented with HTTPS, regular security updates, and firewall protection to ensure safe browsing experience.</p>
